with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider/spaces":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"spaces","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": any ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:4OUDS30AllSpaceSemanticTokensProviderP","text":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider\/spaces","kind":"symbol","title":"spaces","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Provider of spaces semantic tokens to use for link spaces"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/spaces"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"title":"OUDSThemesOrange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"type":"topic"},"doc://OUDS/documentation/OUDS/AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDS\/documentation\/OUDS\/AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","abstract":[{"text":"Something which